THIRTEEN MONTHS IN AN AQUARIUM
âI was born in the Pacific Ocean, close to the coast
of Chile.
I was one of a family of two-thousand
five-hundred and ten.
Soon after our mother and father
left us, we youngsters got scattered.
The family was
broken upâby a herd of whales who chased us.
I and
my sister, Clippa (she was my favorite sister) had a
